tag_list: "future beats" TFBS complexion dreamy Chill "Down Tempo" Invention
title: Invention - Bluffs
description:
After much excitement and anticipation; Future Beats Records are elated to unveil Hallucinature EP from the talented beatmaker Invention. 

As an avid nature-lover from Ontario, Canada; Invention's custom artwork is just as exciting as his music; constantly wondering what incredible  space age woodland and ocean scene he can come up with next. All of his artwork is created with a combination of iPhone apps so make sure you check his work on Instagram // www.instagram.com/inventionbeats

Working off Ableton and a simple Korg SP-170S keyboard in tandem with a nanoKontrol 2, Invention often ventures out into the forest to record ambient sounds with a ZOOM H4n and a pair of Beyerdynamic DT 880's strapped over his head. 

After kickstarting his first sounds with the good folks at @Kolossus-Records, Invention is fast becoming a must watch artist for 2015!

Artwork by Dean Chew from @DarkerThanWax

description:
Sweet Harmony (Ryan's Mix). 

Remix bundle available exclusively on Beatport - http://smarturl.it/mwclomrmx?IQid=soundcloud
